         trigger



       Fcn/Trigger: updates the fancy name in the material table.

	BEGIN
		 UPDATE distribution.pipe_material SET _fancy_name = NEW.shortname||' '||NEW.diameter WHERE id = NEW.id ;
		 RETURN NEW;
	END;

